sequenceDiagram
  participant Player
  participant RitualsList
  participant RitualsReducer
  participant AppState

  Player-->>RitualsList: Player tapped on "Add Ritual" fab button.
  RitualsList->>RitualsReducer: Sends "AddRitual" action.
  RitualsReducer->>AppState: Adds newly created ritual.

  RitualsList->>RitualsReducer: Sends "EditRitual" action.
